<h2 id="chapter-4-the-job-search-reality">Chapter 4: The Job Search Reality</h2>

<h3 id="its-going-to-take-longer-than-you-think">It‚Äôs Going to Take Longer Than You Think</h3>

<p>Let‚Äôs be honest: <strong>the job search is brutal.</strong></p>

