<p><strong>This doesn‚Äôt mean you‚Äôre not good enough.</strong> It means:</p>
<ul>
  <li>The market is competitive</li>
  <li>Many ‚Äújunior‚Äù roles aren‚Äôt actually junior</li>
  <li>Timing matters (some companies hire seasonally)</li>
  <li>Luck plays a bigger role than it should</li>
</ul>

