<p>It‚Äôs not just time. It‚Äôs capabilities.</p>

<p><strong>Mid-level developers:</strong></p>

<p><strong>1. Work independently on well-defined tasks</strong></p>
<ul>
  <li>Don‚Äôt need hand-holding for every step</li>
  <li>Can break down tasks into subtasks</li>
